data.description: Welcome to the charm and convenience of Oak Lawn, where this inviting residence awaits! On the main floor you will find a 3 bedroom with a kitchen and a cozy living room. The second-floor offers a 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom with a kitchen and living room. This second floor is currently housing a long-term tenant contributing $730 per month! Most of the windows throughout the property have also been replaced! The property is enclosed by a fenced perimeter. Ample parking space enhances convenience. Positioned in a highly desirable location, this home boasts the rare status of being a GRANDFATHERED-legal two-unit dwelling, seamlessly blending charm and practicality. Beyond its residential charm, this property is strategically located near shopping centers and restaurants, adding an extra layer of convenience to its already appealing features. Embrace the perfect fusion of comfort, style, and accessibility in this gem.
